<p>YOU HAVE INFILTRATED OUR SHELTER AGAINST THIS BODY'S REQUEST. STATE THE REASON FOR YOUR ARRIVAL.</p>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span>
<p style="text-align: center;">Glacon stands up, recovering from the odd sensation of being forgotten. He glances over to confirm 8-Ball's safety &#8212; right where he was moments ago, picking up loose pixels and recompiling them &#8212; and turns to face the figure.</p>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ff9900; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;; border: #ff6f00 4px solid; background:#ff9900; text-align: left; padding: 2px 10px;">
<p>You- we are here to ensure your safety and security. For your own good, please come with us.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/a-symphony-of-iron-and-steel/glachat-talking.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="100px" alt="glachat-talking.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
