</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/a-symphony-of-iron-and-steel/glachat-talking.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="100px" alt="glachat-talking.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span>
<p style="text-align: center;">The figure glances sharply at Glacon, annoyed with his interjection.</p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div style="float:left; width: 240px; text-align: left; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ff00c4; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;; border: #bf207f 4px solid; background:#ff00c4; text-align: left; padding: 2px 10px;">
<p>I-I'm afraid I cannot say. I am unaware of my own capabilities.</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/a-symphony-of-iron-and-steel/mnemchat.png" style="margin-left: 20px;" width="100px" alt="mnemchat.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: left;"></div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span>
<div style="float:right; width: 240px; text-align: right; margin-top: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px;">
<div style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 10pt; background-color: #ff9900; font-family: &quot;Microsoft Sans Serif&quot;; border: #ff6f00 4px solid; background:#ff9900; text-align: left; padding: 2px 10px;">
<p>Now it's time for me to ask a question. What are you doing here? And what do you know of the <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-5241">Cube</a>?</p>
</div>
<div><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/a-symphony-of-iron-and-steel/glachat-talking.png" style="margin-right: 20px;" width="100px" alt="glachat-talking.png" class="image" /></div>
</div>
<div style="clear: right;"></div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span>
<p style="text-align: center;">The figure's mind is sent into vigorous deliberation.</p>
