<p>WE WISH TO ABSTAIN FROM IMPRISONMENT. THIS BODY AGREES THAT WE ARE NOT TO REGRESS BY RESUMING OUR PREVIOUS FUNCTION.</p>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
